data.description: Well kept, 3 Bedroom and 2 Bath home with tons of updates and a large lot. Living room has a woodburning fireplace and beautiful vaulted beamed ceiling.  House was completely updated when Sellers bought it in 2016, including roof, windows, gutters, water heater, and so much more! Granite counters in kitchen and baths, plus desk area in kitchen, on top of eat-in kitchen. Oversized 2-car garage has built-in shelving. Very convenient SW location close to schools, shopping, restaurants, churches. Easy access to I-565, Huntsville-Madison, Toyota plant, Huntsville Jetport. No HOA!
